{"tid":437634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛炫富網上晒金鏈鈔票","createTime":"2017-10-16T07:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T10:19:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c91be8092ae706f9684c91ab240dca0804081f0","tid":437634,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171016/20184353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171016%2F20184353&d=nBD%2B0oRb4ayqU%2FApFVeel9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b5ae77bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20171016%2F20184353&h=0096eae6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20171016/20184353</a><br />\n<br />\n愛炫富網上晒金鏈鈔票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n94,733<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171016/large/a0402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171016%2Flarge%2Fa0402a.gif&h=fc97b03c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】「煙彈」網購騙案男女主腦是一對新婚夫婦，有中招市民近日在網上起底，揭發男姓張，任職廚師，曾涉傷人案；女姓周，英文名叫Miko，自稱模特兒，本身經營網上生意，經常上載露長腿的相片到Ig等社交平台，而且二人經常炫富，上載穿金鏈（圖）及手持大叠500元的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妻曾涉水晶鞋騙案<br />\n<br />\n據知，女20餘歲，男30出頭，二人今年3月註冊結婚，姓張男子報稱在屯門一間餐廳當廚師，曾涉打人及偷竊案。周女於數年前曾在攝影網站自稱全職模特兒，聲稱曾為婚紗雜誌拍攝封面，並曾登上現已結業的《YES》雜誌欄目「城市驚喜」並接受專訪，亦曾為中文大學攝影學會當攝影班模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n據稱Miko曾在西九龍中心一間飾物店做售貨員，友人指周女甚有生意頭腦，其後經營網上生意，專賣潮流貨品，早年曾捲入一宗網購水晶玻璃鞋騙案，她收下買家2,000多元款項後，買家最終卻只收到一對廉價膠鞋，結果遭受害人在網上聲討圍攻。<br />\n<br />\n友人又稱該宗膠鞋當水晶玻璃鞋騙案令Miko一舉成名，據稱當時Miko在fb聲稱可與廠商合作，為客人訂做一對獨一無二的韓國水晶玻璃鞋，讓女士一嘗當公主滋味，結果吸引不少女士光顧，但受害人支付了2,300元貨款後，最終卻只收到一對廉價塑膠鞋，事後多名受害人向Miko質問，她一律不理更封鎖買家賬戶引起不滿。據網上資料，過去有女士在其網店訂購粉底，但最終只是粉底盒，被批評貨不對辦。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林熊、郭美華  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n夫婦網售加熱煙　 寄手指餅給客　 呃逾百人50萬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n運貨紙盒寫明「biscuit」<br />\n<br />\n有事主怕惹官非無報案<br />\n<br />\n夫婦網售加熱煙　寄手指餅給客　呃逾百人50萬"},{"pid":"7e5b4a42badfdc46f28c868ac8ee17f4ec01623d","tid":437634,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"兩千三買到水晶鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06225976475ec78b5205216b6d55caf257e8b82b","tid":437634,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"廚房佬好撚鍾意金鏈"},{"pid":"610bb0248f113d6f1eaa2b21dc6517108912e33c","tid":437634,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"拉左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadda9d87177c357c3118c5f8deaef957cc2cc03","tid":437634,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"傻仔先攬d咁既鏈出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa7b65fb1fdd42ccc3e135d544b763816b13094","tid":437634,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻仔先攬d咁既鏈出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">隨時</span></strong>著草 / 拿去當"},{"pid":"eed5a8dd82fe09c3181b02f4dc049dfb3598520f","tid":437634,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"晒PAT PAT都得既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://s1.postimg.org/42sppgxv7j/DSC00870.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F42sppgxv7j%2FDSC00870.jpg&h=fd8e4658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/62yjou4dlr/2sjrcn54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F62yjou4dlr%2F2sjrcn54.jpg&h=d8451b9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d778ee25c8019666595915dd1ba4848c41560a1b","tid":